Author: MarieDomRaider
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: Different things can influence your choice of storage solution (security, compatibility,‚Ä¶) but it is always more careful to avoid storing your funds on an exchange wallet. You can keep funds on an exchange wallet (such as HitBTC) when you are trading but it is best to transfer your funds to an offline wallet once you are done trading and only intend to store your tokens. Hardware wallets represent the safest way to store cryptocurrencies and DRT, such as Ledger, Trezor, Keepkey, Safe-T by Archos‚Ä¶ Online wallets like MyEtherWallet, Metamask or Mist are less secure because they are connected to the Internet. We are writing a complete article about the subject really soon: stay tuned!

Author: MarieDomRaider
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: Non-fungible vs fungible Tokens ? ERC20 = each token is SIMILAR -  1 bitcoin = 1 bitcoin and 1$=1$ ERC-721 NFT = each token is UNIQUE - 1 diamond isn‚Äôt equal to another diamond Non-Fungible Tokens are used to create verifiable digital scarcity.  ERC-721 and NFT ? ERC-721 is a free and open standard, describing how to build NFT on the Ethereum blockchain. While most tokens are fungible (like bitcoin), non-fungible tokens are all unique and therefor rare and one-of-a-kind collectables.  With a sensational entrance in the blockchain world - notably with the success of cryptokitties (already 25 million dollars and some rare sold for 250 ETH) - the NFT market is in full expansion! But NFT are not exclusive to cryptocollectibles like cryptokitties. Thanks the constant development of the blockchain ecosystem, the properties of ERC-721 tokens allow applications in many fields like gaming, digital arts, software licenses, advertising or even hotel boooking‚Ä¶  Read more about this booming market: https://medium.com/auctionity/beyond-cryptokitties-pushing-future-usages-of-erc-721-and-nft-1b56a1460ce7

Author: Romuald
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: Auctionity Club Announcement  We absolutely value you, our community, your input and involvement. This is why we created the Auctionity Club.    Ever since DomRaider made its debut in the blockchain world last year, it is your support that has kept us going forward.  As announced in our last story, our team has been doing a lot on the infrastructure of Auctionity to ensure its reliability and scalability as we are pushing forward with the development of the platform, and especially with the much awaited feature, Payment Guarantee, scheduled for the end of June.  Meanwhile, DomRaider has also worked hard behind the scenes to build a reward program and to grow the DRT community. We wish to gather as many people as possible from our community behind our project. This is done in order to support our long term project to completely revolutionise the way people sell and buy at auctions. The launch of the Auctionity Club aims at rewarding our long-term DRT believers for their loyalty and provide them with an exclusive group to join. This Auctionity Club will bring more value to the token and be the cornerstone of the upcoming Auctionity ecosystem.  Today, we are really excited to announce that the Auctionity Club is now live!  The aim of the Auctionity Club is to gather DRT supporter, reward them for their loyalty and encourage them to spread the word and help increase the value of the DRT. Another ambitions of the club is to develop the DRT brand awareness and attract new believers of the DRT to grow the community. We hope you will appreciate it!  Before you visit club.auctionity.com and join us, let us give you a small glimpse of what you will find in the Auctionity Club right now and what you can expect from it later.  This club has been created to reward your loyalty. So by joining the Club, you will become ambassadors of the Domraider Token, uniting and engaging others around our Auctionity project.  Features already available include: - Payment by credit card: buy DRT by card directly from club.auctionity.com - Certification of your account: Get access to new functionalities by certifying your account manually or by credit card - Achievement board: take a look at the steps you have achieved and redeem your rewards - Social sharing: spread the word by sharing our latest news, tweet or retweet to get rewards - Be the first to get exclusive news and your Monthly Report - Following DRT informations (actual price, volume, market cap)  You will also reap the benefits of other great features coming this summer, such as sponsorship, affiliation, contribution by submitting original content to get rewards and become an auctioneer. We will give you more information soon.  Early bird special registration    There is a proverb saying that ‚Äúthe early bird catches the worm‚Äú, which means that whoever arrives first has the best chance of success; some opportunities are only available to the first comers.(Source: Wiktionary)  With that in mind we‚Äôre offering 50 DRT medals to the first certified accounts to the Auctionity club.    We are also offering an exclusive DRT reward for every person whose account is certified by the end of this month. Haven‚Äôt registered yet?‚Ää‚Äî‚ÄäHurry up, click here to join the Auctionity club https://club.auctionity.com/ Join us on our Telegram Group to keep up to date on the latest features and to discuss with the community. We will announce important news there as well. Hope to see you soon! Let‚Äôs socialise with us on the following social media channels: ‚úàÔ∏è Telegram Group: https://t.me/Domraider_Chat ‚úàÔ∏è Telegram News Channel: https://t.me/Domraider_News üïäÔ∏è Twitter @DomRaider : https://www.twitter.com/DomRaider üïäÔ∏è Twitter @Auctionity: https://www.twitter.com/Auctionity ü§ñ Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/DomRaider/ ‚ìÇÔ∏è Medium DomRaider : https://medium.com/DomRaider üíº Linkedin: linkedin.com/company/domraider/ üìò Facebook: Domraider üìô BitcoinTalk: DomRaider thread üì∫ Youtube: youtube.com

Author: TOM47
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: Blockchain application to the Auction Mechanism  Blockchain technology can be used in a variety of ways. DomRaider will develop the technological solution dedicated to the world‚Äôs first decentralized auctions blockchain network. This article outlines the fundamental stages to implement the blockchain mechanisms to real-time management of auctions worldwide.  This process is described from the perspective of micropayment for an ERC20 token available through the Ethereum network. This depiction can be adapted to any other platform. The process unfolds in 3 stages:  Stage 1: Opening of micropayment channel. Each auction participant places a ‚Äúdeposit‚Äù through a Smart Contract, which represents a bid.  Stage 2: Off-Chain exchanges. Exchange of a signed character chain that combines the bid amount and its identity.  Stage 3: Channel closing. Reimbursement of all auction participants other than the auction winner.  It is worth noting that the payment taken to initiate the bid may not represent the total amount, which would allow professional users to participate in numerous auctions (on the basis that they won‚Äôt win all of them). We can envisage payment of a small sum, for example 10% of the target amount, on the basis that a delay in payment by the winning bidder is possible. In the event that the amount is not settled, the user may lose their security deposit and get a bad reputation within the system, which may exclude them from certain types of auction.  https://medium.com/domraider/blockchain-application-to-the-auction-mechanism-9c7f557a8e13

Body: DRT is back at ICO price in Euro, but at 1/3 of ICO price in ETH.  ICO price was 0,1‚Ç¨/DRT , ETH price was whatever ETH was worth at the time of purchase ( roughtly 0,000356 for me).  Domraider has been running and growing well for a few years now, they appear to be the leader in domain name in europe , so the base foundation of the project are solid, this is not an out of nowwhere startup. Their ICO road map clearly stated the main achievement are due in Q1-2018, not much done is Q4-2017 (except hiring a lot of people to reinforcer the already existing team, but that's OK for me. Minimum viable product is due to be released by end of january, so far they are sticking to their roadmap.   Price dropped a lot after ICO because people sold the bounty reward and bonuses for easy free money, which to me was kind of a dumb moove.  Price has seen steady upward action recently but the volume is just isn't there to get enough attention on the project + massive sell wall at 0,0001 & 0,00011 ETH which will take a while to absord with current volume but I expect DRT to really get moving once it break through it.  I think Hitbtch is not helping to get the volume up, not the most popular exchange and the price in only by increments of 0,00001 ETH so price actions only happens with 10% value steps.   I personnaly remain quite confident on this project you just have to be realistic and not expect massive achievements only 3 month after the ICO , look for medium/long term.

Author: Trickyt57
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: Guys please stop dreaming.  The use case for DRT tokens is extremely weak.  Nobody is going to want them.   You were all warned about the multiple failings of the project before launch - things like they sell you the tokens and put it through their profit and loss account, as sale of stock, and in return they say the give you nothing, no profits, no dividend, no votes, no influence - nothing.     There were lots of other failings which I won‚Äôt repeat as you read them before the launch.  To buy the tokens you had to acknowledge that this is not an investment, and that there was no price appreciation promise and that you would never get anything back.  They didn‚Äôt promise you any market for the token.  It was quite clear in the white paper that you contributed the money freely to the company in return for nothing except the DRT token, which was a kind of acknowledgement ‚Äúthankyou for your contribution‚Äù.  It has no more value than the brass war medals you see for sale in every market.  Now you are complaining that its price is below what you paid.  That means you think it is some kind of investment?  They told you that token has no relation to the success of domraider as a company.  You gave away your money, acknowldged in writing that you would get nothing back, that this was no investment, no currency, no cryptocurrency, no security, and now you expect something?  What were you expecting when you bought these tokens?  Did you think ‚Äúoh they just say this is worthless for legal reasons, but in reality, they‚Äôll make me rich, I trust them‚Äù  I don‚Äôt suppose you can realistically sell your tokens.  Probably not.  Who would want to buy them?  You have to put it down to one of life‚Äôs experiences that you can one day tell your grand children.  Before you all flame me, can I ask you to pick any of the so called ‚Äúadvisors‚Äù or ‚Äúexperts‚Äù from the whitepaper, and look at their linked-in or facebook page.   Do they even mention Domraider?  In that alone you have your answer as to what you ‚Äúbought‚Äù.  Except you didn‚Äôt ‚Äúbuy‚Äù anything.  You effectively made a gift to the pockets of a small group of directors.  Good for them, bad for you.

Author: Romuald
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: Existing auctioning platforms are based on centralized systems supported by proprietary, closed source software architectures and share these limitations: Lack of transparency Participants have no assurance that bidders are real and the authenticity of bids is not guaranteed. Closed systems No universal web interface or mobile app, each organizer manages their own access Lack of complementary service offerings  The solution to these limitations is the creation of a new, open and decentralized blockchain dedicated to real-time management of auctions anywhere in the world, online or in a salesroom. Through the DomRaider blockchain anyone can buy, sell or promote their services. The DomRaider project is for the emergence of a full ecosystem. As the blockchain is open and open source, anyone can add to it and provide new functions. Anyone can suggest interfaces or services associated with sales and get paid by getting commission on sales.     If you didn't grab our White paper I suggest you have a look on it for further explanations or feel free to contact our support if you want to discuss

Author: Simonetta
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: Hello, I try to explain you what was not understood of the stretch goals, something quite important was misunderstood. The DomRaider blockchain is a project that a lot of people are working on, and it has many supporters, including people like Eddy Travia or Mougayar, people who believes in designing a worldwide auctions blockchain. Perhaps the word ‚Äúworldwide‚Äù was not understood. Cryptocurrencies have become a way to make easy money, not a way to dream in great projects. More people will receive tokens and more people will be involved in this "worldwide" blockchain. The DRT value will not be given by making it an elitist currency, but by making an ‚Äúexchange currency‚Äù. The more a coin is exchanged, the more its value increases. But you have to think long-term. This is the idea that animates the project, not the idea of making fast money.

Body: Don't want to call it scam but...  Here is my problem  I've bought DRT for 1.03093 ETH 14.09.2017. here is TX: https://etherscan.io/tx/0x4d87696eab86213c0140dad6326580a23c6f8fdb25eefa5cbefda98d8e195d08  As you can see, ETH came to this address also at 14/09/2017 https://etherscan.io/address/0xf1edd222d6d96f076cf008cf2c2c3c736acc70f3  Then I checked my balance in DomRider account and the amount of tokens received was 2573 DRT.  I also have screenshot: https://imgur.com/a/GoPD2 (it is in Russian, but I've maid it generally for myself).  Today I've checked the account again and now I see that actually they for some reason enlisted my transaction on the date of 19/09/2017 and amount received was only 2012 DRT!  And of course, all stretching bonuses (if this two bonuses for 200 DRT each is stretching bonuses) have been calculated as of 2012 DRT not 2573 DRT!  Here is screenshot: https://imgur.com/a/fbkPt  Again, I don't want to call it scam yet, but it seems that there was some manipulation with EUR/USD rates. EUR/USD on 14/09-15/09 was lower than on 19/09. But you know, i do not care - I paid with ETH, ETH was received by DomRider on 14/09, tokens have been distributed on 15/09 at night so I need my tokens on the rate of moment of receiving ETH by DomRider!  And also take the attention on the warning message about that "Ethereum & Bitcoin transaction confirmations may require up to 2 hours.". Ok, up to 2 hours but not up to 5 days!!!  BTW, I already requested our Russian support for recalculating but already 5 hours passed and I still has no answer.  I will claim it scam if meantime there will be no reaction and explanations. Please make this explanations with the link to specific Agreement part where it is indicated that DomRider may destribute tokens on the rate which is comfortable only for DomRider.  UPDATE1: Russian support give me the answer that tomorrow they will solve the problem. OK, waiting. UPDATE2: Still no any changes and corrections. UPDATE3: The problem has been solved. Thank you DomRider support!

Author: Romuald
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: Sorry for later answer.  The  snapping rate depends of the TLD. We have the best rates with ccTLDs like .FR, .DE, .BE and also with other gTLDs. We have thousands of customers who have already use our platform.  In addition, DomRaider is the only dropcatching company with the most TLDs domain names.  Dropcatching is our first job at DomRaider. But I shall insist on the fact that DomRaider ICO is not directly related to domain names. The purpose of this ICO is to create a new auction platform based on blockchain technology. It will be firstly used on our platform, by switching our auctions system to the blockchain network and enlarge this to every business concerned by auctions. An auction platform like the one we are creating at DomRaider will have some significant improvements over legacy systems. For starters, the platform would be scalable, reliable and transparent.  DomRaider‚Äôs technology solution will allow for a worldwide auction platform where users will be able to communicate directly. This provides a far greater user base for auctions, and ensures simple and easy decision making and transaction processing at a fraction of the cost of other auction systems.  And the solution will also provide a very fast and secure platform to process and immutably record bids and outcomes. The infrastructure, as it stands, can provide consensus of bids in less than one second.

Author: Gordonium
Title: DomRaider - Decentralized blockchain auctions in real-time
Body: DomRaider network is an open-source blockchain dedicated to the decentralization of auctions in real time. It will be transparent, reliable, adaptable and interoperable, without compromising on speed. The DomRaider network is not only aimed to register auctions and bids. It is the core of a complete new auctioning ecosystem aimed to provide an innovative solution for all worldwide auctioning players. Live auctioneers, escrow, appraisal experts, delivery services and online auctions providers will all be able to join the network, provide their services and add value to the blockchain.  How does the project create value to the ecosystem and differs from competing projects?  Auctions organized by DomRaider will be the first to migrate onto the blockchain network. Strategic acquisitions carried out thanks to the ICO will accelerate other player‚Äôs involvement and will enable its development. The DomRaider ICO combines 4 key factors for its success. The innovation of groundbreaking technology by blockchain experts. The maturity of an already well-established company and an experienced team. Not just a concept, but a solid roadmap and set-up plan.    DomRaiders DRT token pre-sale will run from August 16th, 2017 to October 12, 2017, and the official ICO sale will run from September 12th, 2017 to October 11th, 2017. ICO participation will run directly from the ICO page of the DomRaider.io official website.      Funds received by DomRaider through the ICO and Pre-Sale will be invested in the following areas:    Company organic growth Blockchain auctions research and development The acquisition of strategic targets to expand the actual use of blockchain auctions     DomRaider will be running a full bounty program from August 30, 2017, until the end of the ICO, on October 12, 2017   The company will allocate 30,000,000 DomRaider Token (DRT) for this Bounty program, distributed as follows: BitCoin Signature Campaign: 30% =9,000,000 DRT ‚Äì This also includes posts published on BitCointalks threads to spread the word. Blog/Media Campaign: 25% = 7,500,000 DRT ‚Äì The aim is to write original articles on media such as Medium, Steemit, Newbium, or any blogs or website relevant. Video content posted on Youtube are also accepted. Newsletters Subscribers: 10% = 3,000,000 DRT ‚Äì sign up to our newsletter and receive DomRaider‚Äôs favorite stories and helpful information. Twitter Campaign - 20% = 6,000,000 DRT (9,000,000 DRT): Obtain real followers, tweets mentioning @DomRaider, RT and like.   Facebook/Youtube Campaign 15% = 4,500,000 DRT    COIN DISTRIBUTION In total DomRaider will create one billion DRT tokens. 350 million (35%) tokens will be distributed between the token pre-sale and the official ICO. 150 million (15%) tokens will be distributed to stakeholders, team members, advisors and community members. 500 million (50%) tokens will be kept in reserve for future use.  MINING All DRT token will be pre-mined, and the company has no immediate intention to create more following the completion of the official ICO.
